high_descs: Turn around and face the desk on the right.
Pick up the pencil from the center of the desk.
Carry the pencil and turn to the left.
Place the pencil in the cup on the back of the short table.
Pick up the cup from the table.
Carry the cup and turn to the right.
Place the cup and pencil on the desk, in the center.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and pencil to a desk.

high_descs: Walk to the back of the chair for the computer desk.
Grab the pen from the desk.
Locate the nightstand to your left.
Place the pencil in the coffee mug.
Grab the mug from the night stand.
Turn around to the computer desk on your right.
Place the mug in front of the chair on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a pencil in a mug to place on a desk.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room. Turn to the desk on your right.
Pick up the pencil from the desk.
Turn to your left.
Place the pencil in the cup on the entertainment center in front of you.
Pick up the cup with the pencil in it.
Turn to the right towards the desk.
Place the cup holding the pencil on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place a pencil into a cup and place it on the desk.
